===Etymology===
Related to {{och-l|漂|to float, drift}}; see there for more.

{{zh-ref|Zhang, Jacques, & Lai (2019)}} propose additional cognacy to {{cog|sit-sit|ʑbrū||boat}} {{cog|sit-jap|ʑmbrɯ||{{q|[[idem]]}}}}, assuming that those are nominalized from a verb ''*mbru'' ("to float").

